title: Queen of the County
description: In this Dateline classic, the matriarch of a prominent pecan growing family in San Saba, Texas goes missing and her caretaker is murdered. Josh Mankiewicz reports. Originally aired on NBC on April 23, 2015.
author: nbcnews.podcasts@gmail.com (NBC News)
